CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 18, 1962, pg. 1 reads: "All-Night Gospel Sing For Drafts Fund-With Rousing support from the audience, this gospeler sang "There's No Secret What God Can Do."
TitMainTitle: Man wearing choir robe, posed with outstretched arms in aisle, singing in Calvary Baptist Church for All Night Gospel Sing for the Charles "Buggsy" Drafts Fund
